---
title: Garlicky Prawns with Mini Roast Potatoes and Walnut-Parsley Pesto
description: There a tapas-y, summer holiday vibe to today's recipe. Prawns bathed in a tomato and garlic sauce feel distinctly Mediterranean. So, no matter what the British weather is doing, here's a plateful of sunshine!
